## Boundary Violation Examples

### WRONG (violation)

```typescript
// apps/bot/src/commands/cultivate.ts
const gain = character.cultivationPoints + baseGain * 1.5;
// Game formula is in a Discord command!
```

### RIGHT (correct)

```typescript
// apps/bot/src/commands/cultivate.ts
const result = await cultivationApi.cultivate(characterId, "STABLE");
// Bot only orchestrates. Rules live in core.
```

### WRONG (violation)

```typescript
// packages/core/src/rules/cultivation.ts
import { PrismaClient } from "@prisma/client";
// Database access in the game engine!
```

### RIGHT (correct)

```typescript
// packages/core/src/rules/cultivation.ts
export function resolveCultivation(
  character: CharacterState,
  mode: CultivationMode,
): CultivationResult {
  // Pure calculation. No side effects. No DB.
}
```

