## Adding New Layers

If a new app is added (e.g., `apps/web-client`), it must:

1. Declare which layers it may import from
2. Follow the same import restrictions above
3. Be documented in `kb/engineering/architecture.md`
4. Have an ADR in `kb/adr/` explaining its purpose
